AnyEvent-HTTP-Socks
================================

This module adds socks support for AnyEvent::HTTP by adding
new `socks' option to all http_* functions exported by AnyEvent::HTTP.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  IO::Socket::Socks
  AnyEvent::HTTP

